description.narrative: The Agricultural Support Programme 2 (ASP2) aims to improve economic returns from agriculture in Bamyan province, Afghanistan. It is an integrated set of activities that collectively address the core challenges of Bamyan's mixed farming system and is designed to focus on ensuring sustainability of results achieved under the first phase of the Agricultural Support Programme.
